name: USCFRating
0:
”Alexa ask My Chess Rating”
”Alexa Open My Chess Rating”
”Alexa Launch My Chess Rating”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my chess rating
des:
This single interaction skill gets the USCF rating for a input USCF member id or name. 
Please note that if the skill finds multiple matches for the input member name or id then you need to again use the wake word and invocation name with new criteria.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
